  <notes>
    Attachment source decision (step 6): the FilePreview surface displays a file that is either (a) already in SPE (driveItem) or (b) loaded into a browser buffer for preview. Inspect the existing FilePreview code to determine which. The `<SendEmailDialog />` wrapper accepts both `spe` and `local` source pickers; configure whichever matches the file's current state. Document the choice in task notes.

    Smoke testing of the migrated flow happens in task 055, NOT here. This task focuses on the code change + static verification (build/lint/adr-check). E2E verification is deferred to the wave-level smoke test.

    If the migration reveals an unexpected wrapper-API gap (e.g., the wrapper does not yet support pre-attaching a `local`-source file from a JS blob), document it in task notes and escalate — but DO NOT extend the wrapper from this task. Wrapper changes belong in Wave 1.
  </notes>

